Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說還真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟有不少老油子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓制邊境可不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有些地方沒壓制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這樣子 馬上又要輪到我們上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博格隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備完畢立刻出發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個目標定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算換班了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 天氣真的轉冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼 不是冷的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你珍藏的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被隊長發現會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在執行任務 交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真有那種混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神出奇好 專門找差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我之前的隊長 光擺著一副架子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別有距高感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種隊伍 還不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時待命 移動目標可能有變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時是等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看作戰會議上怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天之內是定不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這麼冷的天要野管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 期間會維護神通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們幾個?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機修組會依次過來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預定時間是23點整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 沒空睡覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21點整之前自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡覺喝酒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到點前恢復清醒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 挺···
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的口味好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家一直夸莉莉品味獨特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算不上夸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 我要告訴你爸媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道該不該這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有一對老夫婦收留了戰爭中的孤兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 希望送點禮物給孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉之前說錯話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說錯話?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒注意說了句「要告訴他爸媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以過去嗎 雖然那裡有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到點之前回來就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小禮物 以表心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前還是敵人 可能不太好收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們收下了 你們客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你們兩個人照顧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始沒打算照顧他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們自己聚過來了 又不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在更像是他們在照顧我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能一直這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 阿妮婭和大家畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨的時候 他們畫著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅畫···
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個孩子畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算叫她畫點別的 還是只畫戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種世界成了她現在的日常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前不久我們還在攻擊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再湊近點看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出奧秘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是行家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起畫畫吧 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 不能待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再留一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去 記得留時間睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要通青維護了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了 你們猜猜是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你畫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想畫這裡的老爺爺和老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是別告訴他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小孩無法理解莉莉的審美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請要要點心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到艾瑪的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫艾瑪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子們真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望那裡永遠都是孩子們的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是假設
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你現在覺得自己無處可歸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前對遇見的孩子這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時這麼說是想安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也一直在尋找歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把我養大的家裡 也沒有歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方我們很難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼意見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了生存才流落到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒把軍隊當自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 莉莉也覺得軍隊不是自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這支分隊 大家在的地方就像歸宿一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才蓋爾隊長說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「記得留時間睡覺 要通宵維護了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像呼嗦的爸爸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看布雷克兵曹長和蓋伊那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時還挺溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然休伊是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總會有那麼一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每家都有個頭痛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我以前就想要個帥氣的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把這個分隊當歸宿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想拿這種表情糊弄過去 沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手別停聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經決定下一個移動地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡往南120公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在利奧·塔克拉斯州邊上和強襲空母匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓制或破壞王國軍設施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來一個燙手山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6點30分出 發維護在兩小時內結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也把這個分隊當歸宿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到艾瑪的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是只會笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前也是這種孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣笑著就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣什麼事都能忍過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續 繼續 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機修組已經走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有辦法的 大家先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計花一兩個小時 我會追上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 你來幫忙 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見 居然會犯這種錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 偶爾發現你像人的一面也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某種意義上 戰場是最看得清人本性的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是硬派強壯的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了前線也會因恐懼嚇得膽怯 哭喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想像你一樣保持平常心 都裝不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為你拋棄了感情活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得自己變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道這樣子像不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後還能待在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕很難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光靠這對老夫婦太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣的地方還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們能力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總比什麼都不做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才開了孤兒院?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看見那幅畫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的孤兒院裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會畫戰爭血腥場景的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把孩子弄成那樣的人就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們有責任看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓孩子們看到不同的世界 不同的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 好好開車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又發呆撞上了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長像個囉嗦的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧 我受夠孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就到利奧·塔克拉斯州了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能走了 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在掩體裡打我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別退縮 應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毀機槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走那邊 走那塊斜坡上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地雷 斜坡上埋了地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後退 別離開線路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 是想徹底擋住我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這架勢是堅決不讓我們接近設施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那設施裡到底有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘可能撤回去 艦炮射擊要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會摧毀雷區的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 蓋伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好···
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是懸浮器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆一邊喝酒去吧 剩下的交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了蓋伊 那傢伙關鍵時刻搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 身後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台機體···
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後退 要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後替我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭結束 之後的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 安睡在我們面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索萊伊王國軍身經百戰的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈羅德·米勒騎士團總長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國皇帝開恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顧敵我關係 向您的死致以由衷的哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且靜靜收起汝向吾等亮出的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛把敵人的葬禮辦得這麼隆重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是某種宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣傳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲遲不完的戰爭 對方也一樣累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要煽動對方的厭戰情緒 瓦解他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有的人戰死連具屍體都沒留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然隊長不挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但唯獨不吃這個豆子料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在執行任務 交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:14.05,标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1628,910)}{\fad(1000,1000)}靈魂的發火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,99)}你好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}現在安詳地駕鶴歸西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}若非天時與立場將我們阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}怕是不會白刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}而是舉杯共酌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}暢談各自效忠國家的未來
